    <mxCell id="n_note" value="Where it all lives&#10;&#10;• Each PRODUCT (tacticl-core, strategiz-core) is a FULL backend of whatever size it needs — NOT a thin shell. Strategiz is enormous and keeps all of it.&#10;&#10;• The ONE rule: any LLM / AI work routes through the shared arbiter. Everything else stays in the product.&#10;&#10;• Arbiter = ONE orchestrator (durable SessionWorkflow) that SPAWNS a child PipelineWorkflow per build. Shared by all products.&#10;&#10;• Voice WS is the ONLY direct browser→arbiter path (latency). Tacticl only.&#10;&#10;• Deepgram/ElevenLabs touch the orchestrator ONLY. The pipeline is silent." style="rounded=0;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;dashed=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;fontSize=10;spacing=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
      <mxGeometry x="665" y="148" width="305" height="245" as="geometry"/>
    </mxCell>

